      <title>韩国尹在医生罢工中提出“灵活”的反应</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/south-korea-s-yoon-offers-flexible-response-in-doctors-walkout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国总统尹锡烈在政府增加医学生人数计划的长期僵局中提出了灵活性，并就两项可能的让步进行了谈判。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/south-korea-s-yoon-offers-flexible-response-in-doctors-walkout</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 04:14:48 GMT</pubDate>
